{{Infobox Berry |name = Pamtre |image = [[File:Pamtre.png]] |caption = This Berry drifted from a faraway sea. It is now cultivated in the Sinnoh region. |growtime = 5h 0m 0s |harvest = 31 berries |replant = 10% |points = 950 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 30 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 }} '''Pamtre''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a [[Cornn]] with at least 130, but no more than 160 points of dry and no more than 80 points of all other flavours. The [[Cornn]] will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
